FL,350,340,120,260,000,100
PN,34902
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F349A1784288893
OL,3,CFamily's five-year fight for answers
OL,4,Cinto young father's hospital death
OL,6,FThe father was 32 when he died in
OL,7,F2020, but it took years for an inquest
OL,8,Fto take place because the hospital
OL,9,Ftrust initially gave incorrect
OL,10,Finformation to the coroner.
OL,12,FIt was 19 months later that Nottingham
OL,13,FUniversity Hospitals NHS Trust
OL,14,Faccepted it had made a mistake.
OL,16,FKarl had been reliant on pain
OL,17,Fmedication since he was hit by a car
OL,18,Fyears before.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G2/11
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,350,340,120,260,000,100
PN,34903
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F349A1784288893
OL,3,CFamily's five-year fight for answers
OL,4,Cinto young father's hospital death
OL,6,FHis mum Tracy Lee, said: "He ended up
OL,7,Fhaving to have that leg amputated
OL,8,Fbecause it was lifeless. Although
OL,9,Fthere was nerve pain, he couldn't move
OL,10,Fit."
OL,12,FAs part of his treatment, he was
OL,13,Ffitted with a pump which would deliver
OL,14,Fbaclofen, a muscle relaxant, directly
OL,15,Finto his spinal fluid.
OL,17,FHe regularly visited the trust's
OL,18,Fneurosurgery team for refills and
OL,19,Fmaintenance of his baclofen pump.
OL,26,@rD@DO]
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G3/11
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,350,340,120,260,000,100
PN,34904
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F349A1784288893
OL,3,CFamily's five-year fight for answers
OL,4,Cinto young father's hospital death
OL,6,FWhile it's a treatment that works,
OL,7,Fsudden withdrawal can be extremely
OL,8,Fdangerous.
OL,10,FKarl Lee was admitted to hospital in
OL,11,F2020 with symptoms including excessive
OL,12,Fmuscle spasms, shivering, confusion
OL,13,Fand hyperventilation.
OL,15,F"We just weren't listened to"
OL,17,FHis family said he could be having a
OL,18,Fbaclofen withdrawal, but the device
OL,19,Fwasn't checked.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G4/11
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,350,340,120,260,000,100
PN,34905
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F349A1784288893
OL,3,CFamily's five-year fight for answers
OL,4,Cinto young father's hospital death
OL,6,FTracy said: "We just weren't listened
OL,7,Fto. Karl always had a family member
OL,8,Fwith him the whole time, so that's how
OL,9,Fwe knew, because originally they said
OL,10,Fthey'd checked it three times, but
OL,11,Fthey didn't."
OL,13,FStaff initially suspected sepsis and
OL,14,Fadministered antibiotics.
OL,26,@nD@MOUsD@MO]
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G5/11
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,350,340,120,260,000,100
PN,34906
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F349A1784288893
OL,3,CFamily's five-year fight for answers
OL,4,Cinto young father's hospital death
OL,6,FThe ombudsman said: "The symptoms of
OL,7,Fbaclofen withdrawal and sepsis can be
OL,8,Fsimilar, yet staff who were familiar
OL,9,Fwith Karl's dependence on the
OL,10,Fmedication failed to fully investigate
OL,11,Fhis symptoms and consider baclofen
OL,12,Fwithdrawal as a possibility.
OL,14,F"Had they done so, they could have
OL,15,Ftreated him and potentially saved his
OL,16,Flife."
OL,18,FNottingham University Hospitals NHS
OL,19,FTrust, which runs the QMC, initially
OL,20,Ftold a coroner that the pump had been
OL,21,Fchecked and was perfectly functioning.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G6/11
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,350,340,120,260,000,100
PN,34907
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F349A1784288893
OL,3,CFamily's five-year fight for answers
OL,4,Cinto young father's hospital death
OL,6,FHis death was put down to epilepsy,
OL,7,Fdespite Karl not having a seizure
OL,8,Fsince he was 13, and an inquest was
OL,9,Fruled out.
OL,11,FIt wasn't until years later and an
OL,12,Finvestigation by the Parliamentary and
OL,13,FHealth Service Ombudsman that an
OL,14,Finquest finally took place.
OL,16,F"We all know that mistakes happen,
OL,17,Fthat's not the issue here"
OL,26,@xD@AOU
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G7/11
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,350,340,120,260,000,100
PN,34908
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F349A1784288893
OL,3,CFamily's five-year fight for answers
OL,4,Cinto young father's hospital death
OL,6,FRebecca Hilsenrath KC (Hon), Chief
OL,7,FExecutive Officer of PHSO said: "You
OL,8,Fshould have medical professionals
OL,9,Faround you that you can trust.
OL,11,F"We all know that mistakes happen,
OL,12,Fthat's not the issue here. The issue
OL,13,Fis what happens afterwards.
OL,15,F"Because if the medical profession
OL,16,Fdoesn't provide honest, clear,
OL,17,Ftransparent answers, then the family
OL,18,Fcan't grieve and the NHS can't learn."
OL,26,@oD@aOUsD@AOUzD@fO]
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G8/11
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,350,340,120,260,000,100
PN,34909
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F349A1784288893
OL,3,CFamily's five-year fight for answers
OL,4,Cinto young father's hospital death
OL,6,FAt the Ombudsman's recommendation, the
OL,7,Ftrust has apologised to Tracy and her
OL,8,Ffamily and has produced an action plan
OL,9,Fshowing how it will make sure these
OL,10,Ffailings don't happen again.
OL,12,FThe trust said in a statement: "We
OL,13,Faccepted the findings given by the
OL,14,Fcoroner in October 2025, and recognise
OL,15,Fthat there were missed opportunities
OL,16,Fin Karl's care, for which we are very
OL,17,Fsorry.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G9/11
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,350,340,120,260,000,100
PN,34910
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F349A1784288893
OL,3,CFamily's five-year fight for answers
OL,4,Cinto young father's hospital death
OL,6,F"We have carried out investigations
OL,7,Fand changes have been made... and our
OL,8,Fclinical guidelines have now been
OL,9,Fupdated."
OL,11,FTracy said: "It has taken our family
OL,12,Ffive long and deeply distressing years
OL,13,Fto uncover the truth surrounding our
OL,14,Fson Karl's death.
OL,16,F"During this time, we discovered that
OL,17,Fthe trust had provided incorrect
OL,18,Finformation to the coroner, stating
OL,19,Fthat the pump had been checked and
OL,20,Ffound to be working correctly.
OL,26,@qD@IO]sD@MOU
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4         G10/11
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,350,340,120,260,000,100
PN,34911
SC,0011
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F349A1784288893
OL,3,CFamily's five-year fight for answers
OL,4,Cinto young father's hospital death
OL,6,F"This revelation was extremely
OL,7,Fupsetting, as we as a family knew this
OL,8,Fstatement to be untrue."
OL,10,FShe added: ""The ongoing dishonesty
OL,11,Fand apparent attempts to conceal the
OL,12,Ftruth have had a profound and lasting
OL,13,Fimpact on our family.
OL,15,F"The emotional toll - the sleepless
OL,16,Fnights, the tears, and the anguish -
OL,17,Fhas been immeasurable, all while we
OL,18,Fcontinue to grieve the loss of our
OL,19,Fson, husband, father, and brother. "
OL,26,@rD@MOU
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4         G11/11
